---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Bulk Hyaluronic Acid Powder Supplier | Cosmetic Grade 99% Purity | Weiyijie Bio"
  description="High-quality bulk hyaluronic acid powder (sodium hyaluronate) supplier. Multiple molecular weights available, 99% purity, cosmetic grade, complete certifications, 1kg MOQ, fast delivery."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Hyaluronic Acid Powder (Sodium Hyaluronate)</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">High-quality 99% pure cosmetic grade hyaluronic acid powder with different molecular weights for skincare, dermal fillers, and medical applications.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Product Specifications</h2>
            <table class="w-full">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Product Name</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Hyaluronic Acid (Sodium Hyaluronate, HA)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Purity</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">99% minimum (HPLC tested)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Appearance</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">White crystalline powder</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">CAS Number</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">9004-61-9</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Molecular Formula</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">(C14H20NNaO11)n</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Solubility</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Soluble in water, insoluble in ethanol, ether, acetone</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Molecular Weight Options</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">
                  • Low molecular weight: &lt;10k Da<br>
                  • Medium molecular weight: 10k-1000k Da<br>
                  • High molecular weight: 1000k-2000k Da<br>
                  • Ultra-high molecular weight: &gt;2000k Da
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Grade</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Cosmetic Grade / Food Grade / Medical Grade available</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Key Benefits for Skincare</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💧</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Deep hydration:</strong> Binds 1000x its weight in water, provides long-lasting moisturization, plumps skin</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">⏳</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Anti-aging:</strong> Fills fine lines and wrinkles, improves skin elasticity, reduces signs of aging</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🧴</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Barrier repair:</strong> Supports skin barrier function, reduces transepidermal water loss, soothes sensitive skin</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🩹</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Wound healing:</strong> Accelerates tissue repair, reduces inflammation, ideal for post-procedure skincare</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">✨</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Improves skin texture:</strong> Makes skin smoother, softer, and more radiant with regular use</span>
            </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Applications by Molecular Weight</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🔬 Low Molecular Weight (<10 kDa)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Penetrates deep into the dermis layer, stimulates collagen production, improves skin elasticity, reduces deep wrinkles. Ideal for anti-aging serums, eye creams, and targeted treatments. Recommended usage level: 0.1-1%.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">⚖️ Medium Molecular Weight (10k-1000 kDa)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Forms a breathable protective layer on the skin surface, locks in moisture, improves skin hydration immediately. Ideal for daily moisturizers, lotions, toners, and masks. Recommended usage level: 0.1-0.5%.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">⬆️ High Molecular Weight (1000k-2000 kDa)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Provides long-lasting surface hydration, plumps skin instantly, reduces the appearance of fine lines. Ideal for serums, moisturizers, and anti-aging products. Recommended usage level: 0.05-0.3%.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">⚕️ Ultra-High Molecular Weight (>2000 kDa)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Used in medical applications, dermal fillers, viscoelastic supplements for ophthalmic surgery, and joint injections. Medical grade available upon request.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Packaging & Pricing</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Packaging Options</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>100g/500g/1kg aluminum foil bag, sealed and moisture-proof</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>25kg/fiber drum, double plastic bag inside</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🎁</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Custom packaging available (private label, custom sizes, printing logo)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Pricing (FOB China, Cosmetic Grade)</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>1-5kg: $80-$150/kg (depends on molecular weight)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>5-50kg: $60-$120/kg</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>50kg+: $45-$100/kg</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2">Contact us for specific molecular weight pricing and large volume discounts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-200 mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Why Buy Hyaluronic Acid from Weiyijie Bio?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Multiple molecular weight options available (low/medium/high/ultra-high)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">99% high purity, low heavy metals, no microbial contamination</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Complete certifications: COA, SDS, TDS, FDA/REACH compliant, Halal/Kosher certified</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Small MOQ support: 100g sample order available for testing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Fast delivery: 3-5 days for stock items, 7-15 days global shipping</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Free formulation guidance and technical support from our cosmetic chemists</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all mr-4">
            Request Free Sample
          </a>
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-white border-2 border-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 text-green-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
            Get Bulk Quote Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
